# The 4 Best Smart LED Light Bulbs of 2026
## Reviews by Wirecutter
Wirecutter independently reviews everything they recommend. They may get paid to link out to retailer sites, and when you buy through their links, they may earn a commission.

## Why You Should Trust Us
The author has more than 14 years of experience writing about technology, including a decade covering smart-home gadgets at CNET.

## Who This Is For
Smart bulbs are a great option for anyone who wants fast, inexpensive, and easy installation and control of the lights in their home.

## How We Picked and Tested
To be considered for testing, the smart LED bulb candidates must:
* Be standard A19- or A21-style, ranging from 800 to 1,600 lumens (60- to 100-watt equivalent)
* Include an app with on/off control and scheduling
* Offer adjustable color temperature for white-light LEDs
* Support at least one smart-home integration beyond app control (Amazon Alexa, Apple Home, Google Home)

## Top Pick: WiZ 60W A19 Color LED Smart Bulb
* This affordable bulb was a standout in testing and easy to set up, and it includes a collection of fun and useful modes and Scenes.
* $11 from Amazon, $13 from Lowe's, $55 from Walmart (pack of 6)
* Compatible with: Amazon Alexa, Apple Siri Shortcuts, Google Home, Samsung SmartThings

## Runner-up: Meross MSL120 Smart Wi-Fi LED Bulb
* While this bulb works with all of the major smart-home platforms, its solid Apple Home support will be particularly appealing to Apple users.
* $29 from Amazon (pack of two)
* Compatible with: Amazon Alexa, Apple Home, Google Home, Samsung SmartThings

## Best for Simple Control: RCA Smart Wi-Fi A19 LED Bulb
* This dependable smart bulb has a great app and was the top performer at low light levels, but it doesn’t offer as many third-party integrations as WiZ, Meross, or U-tec.
* $25 from Amazon (pack of two)
* Compatible with: Amazon Alexa, Google Home

## Best for Big Homes: U-tec Bright A19 1100LM
* This bulb is brighter than many we tested and uses mesh Wi-Fi to create links among all the bulbs in your home.
* $17 from Amazon
* Compatible with: Amazon Alexa, Google Home, Samsung SmartThings

## Best for Task Lighting: GE Cync Full Color Direct Connect Smart Bulb
* This top-performing, ultra-bright 100-watt-equivalent smart LED bulb illuminates workspaces well for maximum visibility.
* Buy from Amazon, $22 from Lowe's
* Compatible with: Amazon Alexa, Google Home

## Other Smart LED Bulbs Worth Considering
* Govee Wi-Fi+ Bluetooth RGBWW Smart LED Bulb (H6008)
* Philips Hue White and Color Ambiance A19 Starter Kit

## What to Look Forward to
* The redesigned GE Cync Reveal bulbs, which are set to release in the second half of the year and claim to have superior light quality.

